maintext:
ROCKY HILL, Conn. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Tuesday afternoon’s drawing of the Connecticut Lottery’s “Lucky Links Day” game were:
01-02-06-07-12-13-16-18
(one, two, six, seven, twelve, thirteen, sixteen, eighteen)
